description: Welcome to this pristine and fully renovated single-family home located in the heart of sought-after South Riding! Surrounded by mature trees this beautifully maintained home offers charming curb appeal with a quaint front porch. Step inside to a welcoming formal living and dining room that flows seamlessly into the open-concept main level. Wood floors throughout three levels. The heart of the home features a fully renovated, modern kitchen, brand new stainless steel appliances, overlooking a cozy family room with a fireplaceperfect for everyday living and entertaining. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious primary suite with a vaulted ceiling and two spacious walk-in closets. Three additional bedrooms, a full hall bathroom, and a conveniently located laundry room complete the upper level. The fully finished basement adds incredible flexibility with a large open floor concept for a family room, a storage room and a full bathroom. One of the standout features is the expansive screened porch off the back of the homeideal for entertaining or relaxing outdoors. Roof is  two years young  and HVAC under five years. Dont miss out on this incredible opportunity! Master BA shower glass door to be installed 12/5.
